params.pricingData: contains the following inputs:  reserveIn       source reserve balance  reserveOut      target reserve balance  tokenWeightIn   source reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  tokenWeightOut  target reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  swapFee         swap fee of the conversion

contains the following inputs:  reserveIn       source reserve balance  reserveOut      target reserve balance  tokenWeightIn   source reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  tokenWeightOut  target reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  swapFee         swap fee of the conversion

getAmountIn(uint256,(uint256,uint256,uin.notice: given an output amount of an asset and pair reserves, returns a required input amount of the other asset Formula: return = reserveIn * ( (reserveOut / (reserveOut - amountOut)) ^ (tokenWeightOut / tokenWeightIn) - 1) * (10000/ (10000 - swapFee)

getAmountOut(uint256,(uint256,uint256,ui.notice: given an input amount of an asset and pair reserves, returns the maximum output amount of the other asset, Formula: return = reserveOut * (1 - (reserveIn * 10000 / (reserveIn * 10000 + amountIn * (10000 - swapFee))) ^ (tokenWeightIn / tokenWeightOut))
